title: Dana Kellin Gold Circles Necklace
description:
The open circle represents the ideas of enlightenment, strength, elegance and timelessness. A shimmering reminder of the connection between oneself and the universe. Dana Kellin jewelry is best known for its intricate, meticulous wire-wrapping details and high quality materials.

  • Dimensions: 17.35 in L, rings approx 1, .8, .7, .6, .5, .4 in. D
  • Materials: 14/20 goldfill
